quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,"Si kammu oon fettii."
  82,2,"Si ko koode …óe cariima."
  82,3,"Si ko maaje …óe puccitaama."
  82,4,"Si genaale …óeen mbaylaama."
  82,5,"Fittaandu annda kondu ardin'no e golle e kondu leelnuno e golle."
  82,6,"Ehey ma ne…ó…óaŇčke hol ko hoomtuma e joom ma teddu…ď…óo o."
  82,7,"oon tak…óo ma o fotndi ter…óe ma o wa…ó ma potandir…óo."
  82,8,"E kala mba'adi ndi o haaja o feewnir ma."
  82,9,"Ala woni ko on yeddoo…ďe √Īalngu no…ďdi."
  82,10,"Pellet ina woodi e dow mon maleykaaji deenooji."
  82,11,"Teddu…ói binndooji (golle.)"
  82,12,"Hi…ói nganndi ko ngolloton."
  82,13,"Pellet …ďeen …óiggu…ďe he…ďe e ne'emaaji."
  82,14,"Faajiree…ďe noon ina e yiite (jahiim.)"
  82,15,"He…ďe naatange √Īande √Īangu njo…ďdi."
  82,16,"∆Āe ngona wirnatoo…ďe nge haa abada."
  82,17,"Holko anndinat ma √Īalngu njobdi."
  82,18,"Refti holko anndinat ma √Īalngu njobdi."
  82,19,"√Īande fittaandu jogantaaka fittaandu hay hu'unde hu'unde fof ko Alla woodani √Īande heen."
  83,1,"Halkaare woodanii …ďeen ustoo…ďe se'esir…óe."
  83,2,"∆Āeen pe'esnatoo…ďe yim…ďe …ďe …óa…ď…ďa timminaneede."
  83,3,"Si…ďe …ďetanii …ďe wolla …ďe pe'esanii …ďe usta."
  83,4,"E …ďee kan fellitaa won'de ko …ďe immintintee…ďe?"
  83,5,"Woodanii mbo √Īalawma maw…óa."
  83,6,"√Ďande yim…ďe ummanii joom binnde."